Targets stuck with {c_important}Explosive Charges{/c} take {c_number}[{SF_1}*100|x%|]{/c} increased {c_important}{u}Overpower{/u}{/c} Damage per {c_important}Explosive Charge{/c} stuck.

Each {c_important}Explosive Charge{/c} can be detonated by an additional {c_number}[{SF_0}]{/c} |4{c_important}{u}Overpower{/u}{/c};{c_important}{u}Overpowers{/u}{/c} before expiring.
